room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: This is a great company.  You will enjoy any room!  Gold rush is fun because so many puzzles can go on at the same time.  Everyone in our group of eight was constantly working on solving puzzles.

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We had such a great time! This escape room is awesome! Everything is well put together, and the staff is wonderful!! We chose the Gold Rush, and it was challenging but fun! We had to use some extra hints ;-), and we enjoyed a bunch of laughs at our own expense. Highly recommend The Escape Game Dallas!!!

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Had a great time trying to escape the Gold Rush. Staff are very helpful, knowledgeable, and polite. Very fun time. Highly recommend this place to anybody looking for some fun. Hope to be back someday!

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: As a fellow Game Guide from Amarillo, we came to The Escape Game looking for more adventure. We surely found our adventure as we took on Gold Rush and Prison Break! There was so much that we loved but we can’t pick a favorite because both rooms were just amazing! Zach was an awesome Game Guide and was very helpful. Two thumbs way way up! I’d give a 10/10 if I could! We will be back for more!

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: The BEST time ever!  Did the Gold Rush!  Staff was outstanding

room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Tried out Gold Rush this time and have tried Prison Break before - both rooms are of very high quality, and the staff is great!
